Diagram 1 (Correct)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It's good for black to play dansu at 1 before capturing two white stones with 3.
\par
\par Being afraid of pae, some people do not play this dansu at 1, but where can white find a pae threat in the beginning? You should play dansu.
\par
\par Let see the next diagram.
\par }
