Diagram 3 (Black Satisfied)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par When black plays \'a1\'e3, if white connects solidly at 1, black is satisfied to occupy the corner by playing 2.
\par
\par If white plays 3, black attacks white by taking away white's base with 4. It is clear that this is a difficult battle to white.
\par
